## 9. User Data Deletion
If you wish to request the deletion of your personal data collected through Content Multiplier, please follow the steps below:

Send an email to vietemt@gmail.com with the subject line: “User Data Deletion Request”.

Include the username or email address associated with your account.

Specify the type of data you wish to delete (e.g., profile information, email, usage history).

We will process your request within 7 business days and confirm once the data has been deleted.

Please note that some data may be retained for legal or security reasons as permitted by applicable laws.
